data.description: Welcome to your new home at 132 Linden Ave in Bellwood, IL 60104! Priced at $269,900, this charming residence offers 3 spacious bedrooms, 1.5 baths, and a 2-car garage. Inside, you'll find large bedrooms, a finished basement, and sleek stainless steel appliances in the kitchen. The gleaming hardwood floors complement the fresh paint throughout, creating an inviting atmosphere for you to call your own. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this your dream home!
